{"tid":293514,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉會傳言】羅馬欲簽「美斯」頂替「美斯」","createTime":"2017-06-22T08:35:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T05:51:51.000Z","uid":187,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b6397e5ecb2b565e23d9125b1c253632a0324eed","tid":293514,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:35:16.000Z","msg":"【轉會傳言】羅馬欲簽「美斯」頂替「美斯」？<br />\n<br />\n隨著外號「埃及美斯」的翼鋒球員沙拿，與利物浦漸行漸近，盛傳意甲勁旅羅馬正考慮於短期內，簽下新援補充，而他們所相中的球員，就是「瑞士美斯」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沙基利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n在沙拿接近以4500萬歐元的轉會費加盟利物浦的情況下，羅馬打算簽下曾經於國際米蘭效力的沙基利，加強鋒線實力。上季，這名瑞士翼鋒曾代表史篤城上陣22次，期間共收獲4入球2助攻，表現不算突出。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n過去一季，沙拿一共於各項賽事，為羅馬貢獻19個入球和15次助攻，是紅狼軍團的進攻核心，而相對之下，同樣是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">史篤城核心大將的沙基利</span>，發揮卻相當遜色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，所以此子未必能夠成為「埃及美斯」的完美替身。<br />\n<br />\n除了沙基利之外，盛傳薩斯索羅前鋒巴拿迪以及里昂翼鋒加沙爾，均是羅馬覬覦的目標。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://football-italia.net/104510/roma-seek-shaqiri-salah\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffootball-italia.net%2F104510%2Froma-seek-shaqiri-salah&d=QdXelFQ4I9jJvmzBiBI9wv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=4eda44e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">football-italia.net/104510/roma-seek-shaqiri-salah</a>"},{"pid":"f95dcf60421339dafa55d7b05948443cf1c1d70c","tid":293514,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"瑞士美斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65489f88c21ecb892c5022c990a05d439a16bd3","tid":293514,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-22T08:37:25.000Z","msg":"羅馬執到寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b91